{"tid":917380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【成龍娶媳婦】19歲吳卓林加拿大婚禮曝光 與31歲外籍妻子Andi相擁","createTime":"2018-11-26T11:15:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T12:10:12.000Z","uid":22349,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7fa7e8ae6c0b670516ed276a5a9f6d12cd8d39ce","tid":917380,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T11:15:20.000Z","msg":"卓林同外籍網紅Andi今日宣佈已於11月8日喺加拿大多倫多結婚，卓林剛在個人ig上載當日婚禮片段，沒有華衣麗服，只有一對新人同證婚人。卓林同Andi穿上白色衫，<br />\nAndi戴上簡單款白色頭紗，證婚人宣讀誓言﹕「承諾愛她、堅守&hellip;」見卓林望住Andi甜笑，Andi感到落淚，二人交換婚戒後，即興奮擁抱。<br />\n<br />\nAndi留言﹕「Back to Hong Kong as Wife &amp; Wife<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/26/191517_d0cecda514a3e8d9328e4fc3d44f9ea7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2F191517_d0cecda514a3e8d9328e4fc3d44f9ea7.png&h=86cd0661&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"194fc51ec1ff3ccbfd46170caead65d4a39f5632","tid":917380,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T12:08:49.000Z","msg":"嫁女？"},{"pid":"7a42144078f6c81c7c4250876a11601ff22cf383","tid":917380,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"194fc51ec1ff3ccbfd46170caead65d4a39f5632","tid":917380,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T12:08:49.000Z","msg":"嫁女？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T12:10:12.000Z","msg":"成龍取新抱"}]}